{"tid":843492,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑幕】前英超球星控訴　踢中甲被迫打假波","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T10:20:40.000Z","uid":1121,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45468ad35dfff45e5682480760464ee29d6ce637","tid":843492,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"中國球壇經常爆出假波傳聞，最近前英超球星安尼捷比爆料，佢加盟中甲球隊北京北控後，曾經2次教練被要求「唔好咁落力」比賽，懷疑球隊打假波，兩隊向球會反映唔單止冇被理會，之後更被球會打入冷宮，呢位尼日利亞國腳表示已向國際足協作出投訴。 <br />\n<br />\n愛華頓青訓出身，先後效力過愛華頓、西布朗同新特蘭嘅安尼捷比，喺英超打滾超過10年，直到上年夏天登陸中甲加盟北京北控，不過10月份就同球會鬧翻，並且一直被雪藏，到今2月更提前解約。 <br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》爆料，安尼捷比投訴喺北控收到疑似「假波指示」，佢曾經2次被教練要求喺比賽中「not to try」(唔好咁落力)，其中1次發生喺對北京人和嘅「打吡戰」前，當安尼捷比向隊友講呢件事，隊友竟然話：「呢度係中國，我哋要聽指示！」 <br />\n<br />\n安尼捷比之後委託曼徹斯特嘅體育律師Chris Farnell向球會反映，不過2次行動都冇任何回音，反而搞到自己被放入雪櫃。雖然依家佢同北控已經「分手」，不過《每日郵報》指安尼捷比已經向國際足協投訴，希望佢哋會進行調查。"},{"pid":"423272b9abf409f0c01ea2268cab7eb63d3a089d","tid":843492,"uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:51:08.000Z","msg":"呢家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef39f48c4b5bf398f5dc93ae994d19fc317945b","tid":843492,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"你估人仔易賺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee7e639686c4c5707d6f61809ffa08e9ad1d5a0","tid":843492,"uid":14983,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"你出盡力都係廢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255f3ec1a8969366398e806f1950075bdbbdd0f0","tid":843492,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"次級聯賽係咁架啦"},{"pid":"b8bdd73d5f2c531abe746774c1738e1aee8d0481","tid":843492,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"足球就係假架啦<br />\n唔係點會有得賭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6ec5b3a0b32d305411bad99d95e2397ce2bfa8","tid":843492,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"去投訴國際足協<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe3241aaa4f46b7d7006035f2a814a2154e43f0","tid":843492,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dabbead5f4f80d67ed2e4c41492e4fae469081a4","tid":843492,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"中國夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2441d1aca108151706747a0d70be49b68a3f87b","tid":843492,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"要打假波搵個鬼佬過黎倏乜鳩 蚛蟈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2312ee0b2801b0ceca495d3ffff615c474db84","tid":843492,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"曼徹斯特嘅體育律師<br />\n個邊假波黑哨都多<br />\n應該係有一個好律師"}]}